Package: raincheck
Title: Minimal deferred argument testing for R functions
Description: The Raincheck package provides a way to check and clean
  up a function's arguments from outside that function. This allows
  for much more readable function definitions.
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Gray Calhoun <gcalhoun@iastate.edu>
Maintainer: Gray Calhoun <gcalhoun@iastate.edu>
